headline: Maureen Power Sweeny Joins the Exceptional Women Alliance (EWA)
summary: The Exceptional Women Alliance (EWA) is proud to welcome Maureen Power Sweeny, Chief Revenue Officer at RapidScale (a Cox Business company), into its prestigious organization of accomplished, influential women leaders. With more than 40 years of leadership experience as a global C-suite executive and business advisor, Maureen brings unparalleled expertise in revenue growth, operational excellence, and large-scale transformation across technology, cloud, and services industries.

headline: Sinch announces appointment of Daniel Morris as Chief Product Officer
summary: Sinch AB (publ), which is pioneering the way the world communicates through its Customer Communications Cloud, today announces the appointment of Daniel Morris as its new Chief Product Officer. He succeeds Robert Gerstmann, Sinch co-founder and Chief Evangelist, who has served in the role on an interim basis.
